$\\theta$ is any involutory antimorphism of\n$A^*$. This yields an extension of the class of $\\theta$-standard words\nintroduced by the authors in 2006.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Nov 2011 08:26:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 Nov 2011 07:00:45 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 30 Nov 2011 00:58:40 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 31 Jan 2012 15:29:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-02-05"}
