retraction speeds of the loops and the speed of the density enhancements within\nthe loops - presumably exiting the reconnection site.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Nov 2011 15:52:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Jun 2012 20:33:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-03"}
